page.title: 35A day in the life
page.content:
On Saturday and Sunday I went to my dad’s house. I had to be quiet because everyone was asleep. When they woke up they got dressed and went out. Then I had to go home, when we got home we went to the park then I came home and went to sleep.

When I woke up I went to my dad’s again I went to the beach with my dad then I came home and went to bed and I had a really good time.


Pupil-Montbelle School
